    <section class='html-notes'><h2>Funding</h2><div class='html-p'>This Work was supported by the 2024 Far East University Research Grant (FEU2024S07).</div></section><section class='html-notes'><h2 >Institutional Review Board Statement</h2><div class='html-p'>Not applicable.</div></section><section class='html-notes'><h2 >Informed Consent Statement</h2><div class='html-p'>Not applicable.</div></section><section class='html-notes'><h2 >Data Availability Statement</h2><div class='html-p'>The data presented in this study are available on request from the corresponding author.</div></section><section class='html-notes'><h2 >Conflicts of Interest</h2><div class='html-p'>The authors declare no conflicts of interest.</div></section><section id='html-references_list'><h2>References</h2><ol class='html-xx'><li id='B1-applsci-14-11836' class='html-x' data-content='1.'>Ahn, G.; Oh, J.; Yeo, S.; Park, W. Technology for Preventing Industrial Technology Leakage Based on MITRE ATT&amp;CK Framework. <span class='html-italic'>J. Korea Inf. Secur. Soc.</span> <b>2021</b>, <span class='html-italic'>31</span>, 29–38. [<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Technology+for+Preventing+Industrial+Technology+Leakage+Based+on+MITRE+ATT%2526CK+Framework&author=Ahn,+G.&author=Oh,+J.&author=Yeo,+S.&author=Park,+W.&publication_year=2021&journal=J.+Korea+Inf.+Secur.+Soc.&volume=31&pages=29%E2%80%9338" class='google-scholar' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>Google Scholar</a>]</li><li id='B2-applsci-14-11836' class='html-x' data-content='2.'>Kim, J.; Lee, J.; Jang, H. Current Status and Prospects of Industrial Technology Leakage through Cyber Attacks. <span class='html-italic'>J. Korea Inf. Secur. Soc.</span> <b>2021</b>, <span class='html-italic'>31</span>, 7–12. [<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Current+Status+and+Prospects+of+Industrial+Technology+Leakage+through+Cyber+Attacks&author=Kim,+J.&author=Lee,+J.&author=Jang,+H.&publication_year=202