15" class='cross-ref' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>CrossRef</a>]</li><li id='B20-applsci-14-11836' class='html-xx' data-content='20.'>Al-Sada, B.; Sadighian, A.; Oligeri, G. MITRE ATT&amp;CK: State of the Art and Way Forward. <span class='html-italic'>ACM J.</span> <b>2024</b>, <span class='html-italic'>57</span>, 1–37. [<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=MITRE+ATT%2526CK:+State+of+the+Art+and+Way+Forward&author=Al-Sada,+B.&author=Sadighian,+A.&author=Oligeri,+G.&publication_year=2024&journal=ACM+J.&volume=57&pages=1%E2%80%9337&doi=10.1145/3687300" class='google-scholar' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>Google Scholar</a>] [<a href="https://doi.org/10.1145/3687300" class='cross-ref' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>CrossRef</a>]</li><li id='B21-applsci-14-11836' class='html-xx' data-content='21.'>Applebaum, A.; Miller, D.; Strom, B.; Foster, H.; Thomas, C. Analysis of automated adversary emulation techniques. In Proceedings of the Summer Simulation Multi-Conference, Bellevue, WA, USA, 9–12 July 2017; pp. 1–12. [<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Analysis+of+automated+adversary+emulation+techniques&conference=Proceedings+of+the+Summer+Simulation+Multi-Conference&author=Applebaum,+A.&author=Miller,+D.&author=Strom,+B.&author=Foster,+H.&author=Thomas,+C.&publication_year=2017&pages=1%E2%80%9312&doi=10.1002/spe.2133" class='google-scholar' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>Google Scholar</a>] [<a href="https://doi.org/10.1002/spe.2133" class='cross-ref' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>CrossRef</a>]</li><li id='B22-applsci-14-11836' class='html-xx' data-content='22.'>Burns, A.J.; Johnson, M.E.; Caputo, D.D. Spear phishing in a barrel: Insights from a targeted phishing campaign. <span class='html-italic'>J. Organ. Comput. Electron. Commer.</span> <b>2019</b>, <span class='html-italic'>29</span>, 24–39. [<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Spear+phishing+in+a+b