            <div class="additional-content">
                <h2><a name="cite"></a>Share and Cite</h2>

                <div class="social-media-links" style="text-align: left;">
                    <a href="mailto:?&amp;subject=From%20MDPI%3A%20%22A%20Study%20on%20a%20Scenario-Based%20Security%20Incident%20Prediction%20System%20for%20Cybersecurity&quot;&amp;body=https://www.mdpi.com/3093546%3A%0A%0AA%20Study%20on%20a%20Scenario-Based%20Security%20Incident%20Prediction%20System%20for%20Cybersecurity%0A%0AAbstract%3A%20In%20the%204th%20industrial%20era%2C%20the%20proliferation%20of%20interconnected%20smart%20devices%20and%20advancements%20in%20AI%2C%20particularly%20big%20data%20and%20machine%20learning%2C%20have%20integrated%20various%20industrial%20domains%20into%20cyberspace.%20This%20convergence%20brings%20novel%20security%20threats%2C%20making%20it%20essential%20to%20prevent%20known%20incidents%20and%20anticipate%20potential%20breaches.%20This%20study%20develops%20a%20scenario-based%20evaluation%20system%20to%20predict%20and%20evaluate%20possible%20security%20accidents%20using%20the%20MITRE%20ATT%26amp%3BCK%20framework.%20It%20analyzes%20various%20security%20incidents%2C%20leveraging%20attack%20strategies%20and%20techniques%20to%20create%20detailed%20security%20scenarios%20and%20profiling%20services.%20Key%20contributions%20include%20integrating%20security%20logs%2C%20quantifying%20incident%20likelihood%2C%20and%20establishing%20proactive%20threat%20management%20measures.%20The%20study%20also%20proposes%20automated%20security%20audits%20and%20legacy%20system%20integration%20to%20enhance%20security%20posture.%20Experimental%20results%20show%20the%20system%26rsquo%3Bs%20efficacy%20in%20detecting%20and%20preventing%20threats%2C%20providing%20actionable%20insights%20and%20a%20structured%20approach%20to%20threat%20analysis%20and%20response.%20This%20research%20lays%20the%20foundation%20for%20advanced%20security%20prediction%20systems%2C%20ensuring%20robust%20defense%20mechanisms%20against%20emerging%20cyber%20threats." title="Email">
                        <i class="fa fa-envelope-square" style="font-size: 30px;"></i>
                    </a>

